com.zonarsystems.twenty20.sdk.deviceprofile

Class SafeAssetInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zonarsystems.twenty20.sdk.deviceprofile.SafeAssetInfo

  • public class SafeAssetInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by eli.rising on 3/22/17. A NPE-Safe AssetInfo class. Instantiated by Json. Fields with "Default value: " marked are what Moshi serializes them to if the information is not given. Note that null and Empty String are not the same- if the manifest provides empty, it will be set to empty.

        public static SafeAssetInfo buildFrom(Cursor cursor)
                               throws InvalidCursorException
        Creates a SafeAssetInfo from a given Cursor. The cursor is expected to have at least one row, but does not query rows beyond the first for data. Throws a InvalidCursorException if there is a problem with the given cursor (explanation follows).
